{"tid":2420244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（美國兩黨又共識）參議院通過親共聯合國大使Linda Thomas-Greenfield","createTime":"2021-02-23T21:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T09:31:01.000Z","uid":50275,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"c8247700f7c0a7ff72db88a1dc7f60d04891c8df","tid":2420244,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:14:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>Senate confirms Linda Thomas-Greenfield as UN ambassador, despite controversy over China remarks</strong><br />\n<br />\nCruz and other Republicans had expressed concern over a 2019 speech the diplomat gave on &quot;China-U.S.-Africa Relationships&quot; at the Savannah State University Confucius Institute&rsquo;s fifth-anniversary lecture event.<br />\n<br />\nThe speech, excerpts of which were reported by The Washington Post, <span class=\"red\">called Chinese intervention in Africa a &quot;win-win-win situation&quot; </span>in which the communist regime and the U.S. <span class=\"red\">could promote good governance, gender equity and the rule of law.<br />\n</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">&quot;I see no reason why China cannot share in those values,&quot; she said. &quot;In fact, China is in a unique position to spread these ideals given its strong footprint on the continent.&quot;</span>"},{"pid":"186cd42c48dbd24cf17c609a1675a863270f0429","tid":2420244,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:16:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/senate-linda-thomas-greenfield-un-ambassador\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fsenate-linda-thomas-greenfield-un-ambassador&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=a9108d75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fsenate-linda-thomas-greenfield-un-ambassador&h=187804a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/senate-linda-thomas-greenfield-un-ambassador</a>"},{"pid":"673b4f0ed736032e1c9a2b55e2e8ee05c18cab9a","tid":2420244,"uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:20:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2021/01/27/linda-thomas-greenfield-china-biden-united-nations-ambassador/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2Flinda-thomas-greenfield-china-biden-united-nations-ambassador%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=50f9b85e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2021/01/27/linda-thomas-greenfield-china-biden-united-nations-ambassador/</a><br />\n<br />\n條女人係孔子學院演講稱讚過支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBiden&rsquo;s U.N. ambassador nominee to face criticism for past praise of China<br />\n<br />\nThomas-Greenfield was already questioned by multiple senators in private meetings about an Oct. 25, 2019, <span class=\"red\">speech she gave on &ldquo;China-U.S.-Africa Relationships&rdquo; at the Savannah State University Confucius Institute&rsquo;s fifth anniversary lecture event.</span> Several Senate aides said the speech was too optimistic and soft regarding China&rsquo;s policies and intentions in Africa at a time when the U.S. government was trying to shed light on China&rsquo;s many abuses there.<br />\n<br />\nShe called for &ldquo;a win-win-win situation&rdquo; in Africa, one in which the United States and China would work together to promote values there such as good governance, gender equity and the rule of law, according to a copy of her speech I obtained."},{"pid":"d47c67b89ec0971bd66f838ac7f11de1704b8831","tid":2420244,"uid":154486,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:21:39.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人已經wfc美國"},{"pid":"1c1d40faf16de04240b1c3e6a613d0cb021aba6e","tid":2420244,"uid":50931,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:22:25.000Z","msg":"香港國際戰線：贏了，全力支持UN <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac0cdc8314fa954e6b8ab330790883c4ae5a2f9","tid":2420244,"uid":379410,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c399a8d8afd16fbf62b58f99fe54e2561b86e8b7","tid":2420244,"uid":147314,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d47c67b89ec0971bd66f838ac7f11de1704b8831","tid":2420244,"uid":154486,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:21:39.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人已經wfc美國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:32:43.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9177b1034a431ceb801e1db6c0ea6ea7449ee1","tid":2420244,"uid":147314,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:37:34.000Z","msg":"係人都知無侵收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家只係一如所料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ac236ebcbaea66261a16b90b233326da9aba1c","tid":2420244,"uid":147314,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">Chinese intervention in Africa a &quot;win-win-win situation&quot; </span></blockquote><br />\n你老味贏兩次仲唔夠，要贏夠三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1abba3c28f8de327eb17d762107f52fb19960f","tid":2420244,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02